{"tid":1595482,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[十月一] 你升支那旗，我升黑旗","createTime":"2019-09-26T05:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:37:28.000Z","uid":206594,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed12eeec7d3ad6430d39616e0676981941d8e34d","tid":1595482,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"材料：<br />\n1. 長遮<br />\n2. 黑tee （薄身比較好）<br />\n3. 夾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnZL71X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnZL71X.jpg&h=ecf31717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n1. 首先將兩個袖縮入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n83Es12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn83Es12.jpg&h=68f6bf60&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 插把遮入去，衫領位用遮骨攝住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZK2U1m8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZK2U1m8.jpg&h=77089516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 加多兩個夾夾實，防止個袖飛出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hy3kWVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhy3kWVv.jpg&h=f7a69bf9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OH0GGnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOH0GGnd.jpg&h=f22167df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得個遮柄礙眼嘅都可以咁樣放，不過一定要用夾夾實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5X9Qji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5X9Qji.jpg&h=f925f7d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1048359c35c2fcf75359950748638721f3b611d0","tid":1595482,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20